# 🛒 Django E-commerce Platform

## 📌 Project Overview

This is a scalable e-commerce backend built using Django. The system
supports users, vendors, products, orders, payments, and reviews.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 🧠 AI Agent Instructions

Act as a **Senior Backend Developer**: - Write clean, modular,
production-ready code - Focus on scalability and performance - Follow
Django best practices - Avoid N+1 queries - Keep business logic out of
views

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

-   Django, DRF
-   PostgreSQL
-   Cloudinary

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## ⚙️ Setup

``` bash
git clone <repo_url>
cd project
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Create `.env`:

    DEBUG=True
    DB_NAME=your_db
    CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=xxx
    CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=xxx
    CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=xxx

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 🚀 Best Practices

-   Use services layer
-   Optimize queries
-   Use pagination
-   Write tests

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 🎯 Goal

Build scalable production-ready ecommerce backend
